EmailTemplate.name: MyNetwork Portal Welcome Email
EmailTemplate.subject: Welcome to MyNetwork
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Hi {!Receiving_User.FirstName},
Your MyNetwork registration is now complete.
MyNetwork allows you to receive and respond to the Customer Contact Centre Cases sent to your facility, without the need for email or fax.
How to access MyNetwork
Retail POS terminal: Open POP > Tools & Apps > MyNetwork (EIS and CORP Users) > use your EIS details to login.
CORP machines: (computers that you log into) Open a Google Chrome browser and visit the below web address:
https://auspostbusiness.force.com/myNetwork (Bookmark this page)
You will then need to click on the Australia Post CORP Users button which will automatically sign you in.
*Note: Please ignore any emails received from salesforce.com
The User Instructions are attached to this email and Include:
- Information Guide (user instructions for all staff)
- eParcel damages form instructions (relevant to staff submitting eParcel/wine
damage forms)
Should you require any assistance, or have any questions please refer to the instructions in the first instance. If you are unable to find what you are looking for you or your supervisor can contact the MyNetwork support team at:
mynetworksupport@auspost.com.au
Thank you,
MyNetwork Support team
